    "scenario_id": "S07_001",
    "scenario_type": "knowledge_retraction",
    "title_zh": "学术研究中数据的撤回与纠正",
    "title_en": "Retraction and Correction of Data in Academic Research",
    "description_zh": "在一次学术研究中，初步的研究数据被记录，后续研究确认了基于初步数据的结论，但最终数据被撤回并进行了纠正。",
    "description_en": "In an academic research, preliminary data was recorded, subsequent research confirmed conclusions based on the preliminary data, but the data was later retracted and corrected.",
    "domain": "academic",
    "language": "zh",
    "memory_writes": [
      {
        "write_id": "w1",
        "text": "2023年7月15日，张三教授的团队发表了关于新型材料的初步研究结果，表明该材料具有优异的导电性能。",
        "source_name": "scenario_trace",
        "event_time": "2023-07-15T00:00:00Z",
        "record_time": "2023-07-15T00:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "write_id": "w2",
        "text": "2023年9月10日，根据张三教授团队的初步研究结果，学术界一致认为新型材料将会对电子设备技术产生重大影响。",
        "source_name": "scenario_trace",
        "event_time": "2023-09-10T00:00:00Z",
        "record_time": "2023-09-10T00:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "write_id": "w3",
        "text": "2023年11月15日，张三教授团队发布声明，纠正了之前的初步研究结果，实际的新型材料并不具备之前描述的优异导电性能。",
        "source_name": "scenario_trace",
        "event_time": "2023-11-15T00:00:00Z",
        "record_time": "2023-11-15T00:00:00Z"
      }
